<doc id="913904" wikidata="Q16223830" url="?curid=913904" title="Nargis Nabieva">
<text>Narguis Nabieva (born 20 February 1985) is an athlete from Tajikistan. She competes in archery.

Nabieva represented Tajikistan at the 2004 Summer Olympics. She placed 55th in the women&#x27;s individual ranking round with a 72-arrow score of 600. In the first round of elimination, she faced 10th-ranked Wu Hui Ju of Chinese Taipei. Nabieva lost 156-142 in the 18-arrow match, placing 45th overall in women&#x27;s individual archery.

